title: 820-3787-A no USB from both ports
message: Check if USB_EXTB_OC_L and USB_EXTA_OC_L are high. Disconnect right IO board and see if USB on the board has power.

title: 820-3787-A no USB from both ports
message: USB_EXTA_OC_L = 0.024 on U4600 and USB_EXTB_OC_L = 3.022 pin 3 on J9510

title: 820-3787-A no USB from both ports
message: That means that J4600 is drawing too much current. Either a short on the 5V line from U4600 to J4600 or dead U4600.
